summary: Margherita preset for Racemenu. She is a Nord.
descriptionHtml:
[center]If you like Margherita, [b][color=#ff0000]don't miss her gorgeous sister Maddalena![/color][/b] http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76283/?[/center][center]
This is the Racemenu preset of Margherita, one of my first characters.
Margherita is a Nord[/center]
[u]Installation[/u]
Extract Margherita.jslot to your Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets
Go into game, tab "showracemenu" with the console, select Nord race and then choose Margherita in the Presets list. Done.

[u]Requirements[/u]
Skyrim.esm (obviously)
SKSE (obviously) http://skse.silverlock.org/
Racemenu (obviously) http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?
SG Female Eyebrows http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?
KS Hairdo's Renewal http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?
[size=4][u][b]I strictly reccomend Leyenda skin[/b][/u]  http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73512/?
and [u]Snapdragon Prime ENB [/u]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70451/?
if you want [u]this kind of result in your game[/u][/size]

[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/G3sO3aj.jpg[/img][/center]
[u]Reccomended[/u]
You need this mods if you want her look 100% as in the screenshots
For the body: Unpb  http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900/?
For the skin: Leyenda skin http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/73512/?
For the Eye reflection:RAns Eye Reflextion Extender  http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20343/?
Enb: Snapdragon Prime ENB http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70451/?
Armors: TERA armors Collection for Unp http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25846/?

[u]Permissions[/u]
If someone wants to make her a follower, please, inform me before. Thank you.[left][/left][center][img]http://i.imgur.com/2AFz4Tq.jpg[/img]
